snippet.title: Rest your very best! | Pokémon Sleep
snippet.description:
Place your smartphone by your pillow, then go to sleep. Just like that, waking up in the morning becomes something to look forward to with Pokémon Sleep! 

Keep it up every day and rest your very best when Pokémon Sleep arrives in Summer 2023!
